            <a href="https://link.msgsndr.com/widget/booking/ZIYe8XGFfENxqvZHGTBD" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition self-center" data-t-es="Agendar Ahora" data-t-en="Book Now">Agendar Ahora</a>
