        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden min-h-[260px] text-white">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/img/services/Cheekbone-lift.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/55"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 p-6 flex flex-col h-full text-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl mb-2" data-t-es="MEJILLAS" data-t-en="CHEEKS">MEJILLAS</h3>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-white/90 mb-4">
                <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/70"></span>
                <span data-t-es="Típicamente 2-3 jeringas" data-t-en="Typically 2-3 syringes">Típicamente 2-3 jeringas</span>
                <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/70"></span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/90 mb-4" data-t-es="Agregar relleno y soporte a las mejillas incrementa el volumen, define los pómulos y puede mejorar la apariencia de la parte inferior del rostro." data-t-en="Adding filler and support to your cheeks will increase volume and define your cheekbones and can improve the appearance of the lower face as well.">Agregar relleno y soporte a las mejillas incrementa el volumen, define los pómulos y puede mejorar la apariencia de la parte inferior del rostro.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://link.msgsndr.com/widget/booking/ZIYe8XGFfENxqvZHGTBD" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition self-center" data-t-es="Agendar Ahora" data-t-en="Book Now">Agendar Ahora</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden min-h-[260px] text-white">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/img/services/Puppet-lines.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/55"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 p-6 flex flex-col h-full text-center">
            <div>
